00:04:04.762 --> 00:04:07.355
in tsayt onfang krig in Kretinge,

00:04:07.547 --> 00:04:09.533
oykh fun di litvishe rotskhim.

00:04:09.352 --> 00:04:11.709
ir gedenkt dem monat, mer-veyniker?

00:04:11.563 --> 00:04:13.414
umgefer in SINTYABR'.

00:04:14.634 --> 00:04:19.708
akhuts di muter un dem, der foter, hot ir gehat oykh a bruderl?

00:04:18.836 --> 00:04:20.535
a bruder, Yoysef.

00:04:19.781 --> 00:04:21.193
