00:04:20.608 --> 00:04:21.750
Yoysef.

00:04:21.907 --> 00:04:25.929
er iz gev- geborn in toyznt nayn hundert zibn in tsvantsikstn yor.

00:04:25.929 --> 00:04:30.019
