00:04:33.163 --> 00:04:34.862
a babe, Basye

00:04:34.985 --> 00:04:36.431
Mendelovitsh.

00:04:36.521 --> 00:04:38.754
shoyn a eltere froy geven dan,

00:04:38.782 --> 00:04:42.945
oykh umgekumen, derharget tsuzamen mit di muter mitn bruder tsuzamen.

00:04:43.102 --> 00:04:43.923
in

00:04:43.322 --> 00:04:45.139
bay undz in shtetl, in Kretinge.

00:04:44.688 --> 00:04:46.049
Kretinge, Lite.

00:04:45.650 --> 00:04:46.589
Lite.

00:04:48.249 --> 00:04:56.630
zayt azoy gut yetst, dertseylt mir, filt zikh fray tsu dertseyln v- ayere, ale ayere zikhroynes fun der heym, vu hot ir gevoynt,

00:04:57.328 --> 00:04:58.746
vi hot zikh gelebt,

00:04:58.746 --> 00:05:01.355
vi hot zikh gelernt? alts vos ir gedenkt, bite.

00:05:01.192 --> 00:05:02.233
bizn krig.

00:05:01.985 --> 00:05:03.043
bizn krig.

00:05:04.685 --> 00:05:11.601
nu, mir hobn gelebt in (ksh-) Kretinge, ge- geven gants farmeglekhe mentshn, gehat a shtub a eygene.

00:05:11.601 --> 00:05:14.889
der foter hot gehat a eygene land-virtshaft

00:05:15.030 --> 00:05:16.158
mit a

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:18.466
nu, tsigelnye hot men dos gerufn mit,

00:05:18.962 --> 00:05:23.648
geven arbeter dortn, un er hot ongefirt mit, mit der arbet.

00:05:24.665 --> 00:05:29.182
in shtub vos zayn- di ma- di muter iz geven a shtubike baleboste.

00:05:29.238 --> 00:05:31.021
geven in shtub a

00:05:31.314 --> 00:05:33.165
a mol hot men dos gerufn a dinst,

00:05:35.212 --> 00:05:37.036
un mir hobn, kinder hobn gelernt.

00:05:37.036 --> 00:05:39.293
gegangen in folkshul. ikh bin gegangen

00:05:39.293 --> 00:05:43.222
in a hebreishe TARBUT-folkshul iz geven bay undz in shtetl,

00:05:43.397 --> 00:05:45.889
fir (MAKHLOKAs) geendikt dortn.

00:05:46.215 --> 00:05:48.487
mayn bruder hot oykh dortn gelernt.

00:05:48.543 --> 00:05:51.035
nor er hot nit bavizn shoyn tsu endikn.

00:05:51.952 --> 00:05:54.573
nu, bay undz iz n- alts oyf ivrit.

00:05:54.573 --> 00:05:57.785
ikh gedenk nokh di lerers vos zaynen geven bay undz in

00:05:57.977 --> 00:06:00.311
shule. er iz geven, kontik a (busl)

00:06:00.311 --> 00:06:01.768
fun di frume.

00:06:01.925 --> 00:06:03.826
familye iz geven Dubitski.

00:06:04.203 --> 00:06:07.944
ir hot men ge- di ler- di froy hot men gerufn Miryem Dubitski.

00:06:08.169 --> 00:06:11.271
dem, un der man irer, gedenk ikh nit di familye.

00:06:11.271 --> 00:06:12.427
zey hobn gehat a zun

00:06:12.427 --> 00:06:13.609
ELITSUR.

00:06:13.637 --> 00:06:14.661
dos gedenk ikh (nokh).

00:06:14.767 --> 00:06:16.840
di lererke, Miryem Dubitski

00:06:16.840 --> 00:06:19.048
lebt nokh biz haynt in Yerusholaim.

00:06:19.614 --> 00:06:20.154
(ober)

00:06:19.695 --> 00:06:21.461
zey zenen aroysgeforn fun...

00:06:20.792 --> 00:06:23.588
shoyn aroysgeforn farn krig nokh a mol

00:06:24.082 --> 00:06:25.123
fun Lite.

00:06:25.922 --> 00:06:33.091
kh'volt aykh nor gevolt betn, zayt azoy gut. ir hot gezogt ir hot gehat a, a shtub far zikh aleyn.

00:06:32.402 --> 00:06:33.055
ye.

00:06:33.093 --> 00:06:36.254
vi groys iz geven ayer shtub? vifl tsimern hot ir gehat dortn?

00:06:36.254 --> 00:06:37.931
mer-veyniker, oyb ir gedenkt.

00:06:37.230 --> 00:06:38.843
s'iz geven fir tsimern.

00:06:39.017 --> 00:06:41.897
ir hot gehat a bazundern tsimer far zikh aleyn?

00:06:41.040 --> 00:06:45.778
ye, ikh mitn bruder hobn gehat a tsimer. nakher iz geven aza es-tsimer.

00:06:46.121 --> 00:06:48.413
(se fleg) a mol, (hot men) gerufn a salon,

00:06:48.413 --> 00:06:51.246
un a shlof-tsimer fun di eltern. a kikh.

00:06:51.723 --> 00:06:54.012
mir hobn gehat, in shtub iz geven a dinst.

00:06:54.930 --> 00:06:56.426
m'hot gelebt nit-shlekht.

00:06:56.178 --> 00:06:58.569
di dinst iz geven nisht keyn yidishe?

00:06:57.818 --> 00:06:59.538
neyn, a litvishe, ye.

00:06:59.543 --> 00:07:00.190
m'hot ir gerufn K-

00:06:59.604 --> 00:07:03.918
un vos far a batsiungen iz geven tsvishn ayer mishpokhe un di dinst, gedenkt ir?

00:07:04.245 --> 00:07:07.760
nu, nit shlekht, nit shlekht. a g- fayne g- fayne,

00:07:07.760 --> 00:07:09.724
KAROLINA hot men ir gerufn.

00:07:09.780 --> 00:07:12.643
nokhn krig az ikh bin gekumen hob ikh ir nokh getrofn

00:07:12.935 --> 00:07:14.347
(un) geven bay ir.

00:07:15.028 --> 00:07:15.832
nu

00:07:16.665 --> 00:07:27.223
yetst dertseylt mir a bisl vayter vegn lernen. vi iz geven in di shule? ir hot gehat khavertes, khaver, KHAVERIM? vi iz, ir hot geg-, ir hot gehert tsu epes a sport-klub?

00:07:27.414 --> 00:07:33.284
in l- az mir hobn gelernt in di hebreishe folkshul iz geven farshteyt zikh KHAVERIM un KHAVEROT.

00:07:33.287 --> 00:07:35.188
ale zaynen mir geven yidishe.

00:07:35.497 --> 00:07:36.571
un me fl-

00:07:36.729 --> 00:07:40.540
me fleg geyn in a klub. ikh perzenlekh bin gegan (eyn) tsayt nit lang

00:07:40.540 --> 00:07:42.832
in Makabi, in a sport-klub.

00:07:43.416 --> 00:07:44.518
(un dortn fleg-)

00:07:43.462 --> 00:07:45.397
mit vos flegt ir zikh shpiln?

00:07:44.539 --> 00:07:47.962
far, ikh fleg far, ikh fleg f- farnemen zikh pingpong.

00:07:48.710 --> 00:07:50.797
bay undz hot men, a mol hot men es gerufn pingpong.

00:07:51.191 --> 00:07:52.637
haynt ruft men dos oykh UNK.

00:07:52.187 --> 00:07:53.059
haynt, haynt oykh?

00:07:53.672 --> 00:07:57.750
nu, s'iz geven yung, m'iz geven yung. hot men, s'iz geven heymlekh.

00:08:00.253 --> 00:08:05.857
vi volt ir zi- az ir vilt zikh dermanen vi s'hot zikh gelebt yene tsaytn ekonomish,

00:08:05.857 --> 00:08:11.967
farglaykhn mit hayntike tsaytn, vi, vi, vi hot zikh ayer familye ah, gelebt dort ekonom-

00:08:11.053 --> 00:08:14.777
nu, undzer familye perzenlekh hobn gelebt ekonomish nit-shlekht.

00:08:15.035 --> 00:08:17.285
geven farshidene shikhtn dan oykhet.

00:08:17.313 --> 00:08:20.801
gele- f- geven farshidene in shtetl bay undz, farshidene shikhtn.

00:08:20.958 --> 00:08:23.096
nor mir hobn gelebt nit-shlekht.

00:08:24.603 --> 00:08:27.449
s'iz geven a sakh yidishe familyes in ayer shtetl?

00:08:28.620 --> 00:08:32.363
s'iz geven nit-veynik, nit-veynik. genoy veys ikh nit, ober s'iz geven a shtetl

00:08:32.382 --> 00:08:33.861
kimat fun yidn

00:08:34.339 --> 00:08:38.113
un yidishe balebatim. m'hot gehat hayzer, m'hot gehat fabriklekh.

00:08:39.334 --> 00:08:43.412
yetst redndik vegn yidishn lebn in ayer shtetl far der milkhome,

00:08:44.617 --> 00:08:52.663
lomir aykh fregn vegn religyezn lebn. vos gedenkt ir vegn dem, vegn (religye) vos far a religyeze lebn iz geven in ayer familye?

00:08:50.974 --> 00:08:52.017
ikh vey-

00:08:52.194 --> 00:08:55.929
in undzer familye, mir zaynen ge- s'iz geven a koshere yidishe shtub.

00:08:55.974 --> 00:08:58.470
der foter iz nit geven keyn sh-

00:08:58.470 --> 00:09:02.089
keyn, aza frumer. nor shabes flegt men geyn in shul

00:09:02.117 --> 00:09:03.709
un yontoyvim

00:09:03.753 --> 00:09:08.240
un f- fraytik ovnt flegt men geyn in shul, un me fleg kumen fun shul.

00:09:08.240 --> 00:09:10.481
di muter flegt ale mol bentshn likht.

00:09:10.655 --> 00:09:13.319
(s'hot) geshpirt azoy a yidishe shtub a,

00:09:13.319 --> 00:09:14.753
m'hot gehaltn fun

00:09:14.753 --> 00:09:15.914
yidishn din.

00:09:17.169 --> 00:09:18.783
m'hot, s'iz geven kosher.

00:09:19.785 --> 00:09:23.981
no- un ikh hob geendikt di folkshul di TARBUT,

00:09:24.088 --> 00:09:27.131
bin ikh aribergegangen lernen vayter

00:09:27.131 --> 00:09:29.409
in a litvishe gimnazye in

00:09:29.420 --> 00:09:31.033
KLAIPĖDA oyf litvish.

00:09:31.033 --> 00:09:32.030
tsu Meml.

00:09:32.627 --> 00:09:35.423
dos iz geven fir un tsvantsik kilometer fun Kretinge.

00:09:36.896 --> 00:09:38.741
nu, dortn hob ikh gelernt

00:09:38.752 --> 00:09:40.046
eyn yor.

00:09:43.713 --> 00:09:48.444
dortn hob ikh gelernt eyn yor bizn nayn un draysikstn merts,

00:09:48.455 --> 00:09:50.275
biz Hitler iz arayn in

00:09:50.275 --> 00:09:51.099
Meml.

00:09:52.016 --> 00:09:53.819
dan hot men gemuzt shoyn farlozn K-

00:09:53.819 --> 00:09:54.738
Meml.

00:09:54.783 --> 00:09:58.223
un (bin) ariber lernen in Kretinge. hot men ofn gemakht oykh

00:09:58.223 --> 00:10:00.279
a gimnazye far meydlekh.

00:10:01.112 --> 00:10:03.783
vos (es) hobn geven di unterrikhter meystn

00:10:03.783 --> 00:10:04.970
unter di,

00:10:05.638 --> 00:10:07.947
unter di galokhim bay undz in shtetl.

00:10:07.947 --> 00:10:10.117
zikh ongerufn PRANCIŠKONAI.

00:10:13.346 --> 00:10:16.361
azoy az mir, dos (iz) geven bizn fertsikstn yor.

00:10:16.805 --> 00:10:21.527
lernendik zikh in der gimnazye vos ir dermant, in der Frantsiskaner gimnazye,

00:10:21.527 --> 00:10:23.263
s'iz geven a katolishe avade.

00:10:22.530 --> 00:10:23.720
katolishe, ye.

00:10:23.640 --> 00:10:31.701
hot ir epes gefilt als yidish meydl a untershid? (tsi) ir hot gefilt epes antisemitishkeyt, (hobn)...

00:10:30.490 --> 00:10:32.715
neyn, ken aykh nit zogn, neyn, (V OBSHCHEM)

00:10:32.280 --> 00:10:33.101
neyn.

00:10:32.715 --> 00:10:38.281
neyn. geven nit ikh aleyn, zaynen geven nokh a finf zeks meydlekh zaynen mir geven yidishe,

00:10:34.035 --> 00:10:35.768
s'iz geven nokh yidishe meydlekh?

00:10:38.405 --> 00:10:41.184
un m'hot nit geshpirt dortn azoy.

00:10:41.578 --> 00:10:42.554
efntlekh.

00:10:42.554 --> 00:10:44.154
vos zey hobn geklert in zikh

00:10:44.632 --> 00:10:45.639
veysn mir nit.

00:10:46.168 --> 00:10:48.376
dort hot ir zikh gelernt biz

00:10:48.376 --> 00:10:49.757
nayntsn hundert...

00:10:49.650 --> 00:10:51.180
fertsik, biz...

00:10:50.606 --> 00:10:53.317
vos, vos hot pasirt in nayntsn hundert fertsik?

00:10:53.289 --> 00:10:55.902
dan zaynen arayn bay undz di sovyetn

00:10:55.902 --> 00:10:57.469
in Lite gekumen.

00:10:57.677 --> 00:11:00.506
dan hot zikh altsding gebitn, zikh ofn gema-,

00:11:00.933 --> 00:11:04.691
dan z- hot zikh ofn gemakht a, oykh a melukhishe shul shoyn,

00:11:05.118 --> 00:11:07.846
un zey hobn ge- shoyn gelernt ale tsuzamen,

00:11:08.375 --> 00:11:10.448
yinglekh mit meydlekh tsuzamen,

00:11:10.448 --> 00:11:13.584
un in di shul hob ikh gelernt bizn onfang fun krig.

00:11:14.332 --> 00:11:16.588
hob ikh geendikt in di shul zibn klasn.

00:11:16.712 --> 00:11:19.288
dos iz shoyn far di shove- sovyetishe tsaytn.

00:11:17.759 --> 00:11:19.618
far di sovyetishe makht, ye.

00:11:19.749 --> 00:11:22.258
bikhlal volt ikh aykh gevolt betn

00:11:22.314 --> 00:11:24.294
tsu farglaykhn dos lebn

00:11:24.294 --> 00:11:26.387
biz di sovyetn arayn un

00:11:26.398 --> 00:11:29.008
in di kurtse tsayt vos di sovyetn zaynen geven.

00:11:29.857 --> 00:11:35.943
ir kent farglaykhn un dertseyln a bisl vos far a enderungen hot zikh gefilt demolst. vos ir gedenkt fun yene tsaytn.

00:11:36.810 --> 00:11:38.323
perzenlekh bay undz?

00:11:38.160 --> 00:11:40.517
bikhlal, perzenlekh un bikhlal.

00:11:38.602 --> 00:11:40.563
nu, bikhlal, nu,

00:11:40.623 --> 00:11:44.397
nu, s'hot geshpirt farshteyt zikh, zikh glaykh gebitn der gantser

00:11:44.522 --> 00:11:45.799
rezhim.

00:11:46.226 --> 00:11:47.148
m'hot dos

00:11:47.593 --> 00:11:51.092
di, m'hot natsyonalizirt bay mentshn glaykh az alts,

00:11:51.120 --> 00:11:53.437
za- gesheftn, hayzer,

00:11:53.448 --> 00:11:56.447
un s'iz gevorn, m'hot genumen aroysfirn

00:11:56.992 --> 00:12:00.221
in Sibir zeyer a sakh, umgefer undzer mishpokhe oykh,

