00:22:23.038 --> 00:22:24.107
arum

00:22:24.152 --> 00:22:26.081
iz geshtanen harmatn

00:22:26.081 --> 00:22:28.415
arumgeshtelt a- arum un arum.

00:22:29.113 --> 00:22:30.052
un zey hobn

00:22:30.564 --> 00:22:32.246
eyner hot gemoldn

00:22:32.471 --> 00:22:34.417
fun fertsn yor

00:22:34.445 --> 00:22:36.206
biz fertsik yor

00:22:36.217 --> 00:22:37.700
zol geyn oyf di zayt.

00:22:37.700 --> 00:22:39.345
a makh geton mit di hant

00:22:39.345 --> 00:22:41.780
un bavizn oyf di zayt zol men geyn.

00:22:42.292 --> 00:22:44.936
farshteyt zikh, mentshn hobn zikh dershrokn. m'hot shoyn epes a,

00:22:45.380 --> 00:22:47.214
hobn ale, m'hot genumen loyfn

00:22:47.338 --> 00:22:48.800
oyf di gute zayt.

00:22:49.262 --> 00:22:50.550
un mir zaynen oykh ge-

00:22:50.550 --> 00:22:52.715
genumen loyfn. mir zaynen oykh ariber.

00:22:52.907 --> 00:22:55.416
un zey hobn opgetseylt finf hundert,

00:22:56.045 --> 00:22:57.761
m'hot opgehakt mit di hant.

00:22:57.902 --> 00:22:58.656
genug.

00:22:59.927 --> 00:23:03.516
di finf hundert hot men avekgeshtelt in an ander zayt.

00:23:03.690 --> 00:23:05.946
m'hot oysgeshtelt tsu fir, tsu finf,

00:23:06.677 --> 00:23:09.827
un m'hot undz avekgefirt tsu fus in Telzh, in shtetl.

00:23:10.018 --> 00:23:12.639
dortn iz shoyn geven tsugegreyt a geto

00:23:12.639 --> 00:23:15.041
mit shtakhl-drot arumgetsamt,

00:23:15.654 --> 00:23:17.994
un dortn hot men undz gebrakht, un di iberik-

00:23:17.308 --> 00:23:18.501
velkhe shtot?

00:23:18.253 --> 00:23:19.243
TELŠIAI.

00:23:20.447 --> 00:23:24.860
un di iberike vos zaynen geblibn in GERULIAI hot men alemen oysgeshosn.

00:23:25.661 --> 00:23:27.900
fun vanet hobn mir az- alts gevust?

00:23:28.057 --> 00:23:30.195
far nakht, shoyn gants shpet

00:23:30.352 --> 00:23:33.384
zaynen nor gekumen tsvey meydlekh oyf a fur

00:23:33.710 --> 00:23:34.784
tsu forn.

00:23:35.128 --> 00:23:38.497
zaynen geven oykh khavertes undzere. di familye Telzher.

00:23:38.570 --> 00:23:41.107
eyne iz geven Mikhal Yazh- Yazhgur.

00:23:41.107 --> 00:23:42.260
tsvey shvesters.

00:23:43.650 --> 00:23:45.821
di mame hot zikh vi nit iz dortn

00:23:46.063 --> 00:23:47.947
tsuzamengeredt mit di banditn.

00:23:49.218 --> 00:23:49.983
nu,

00:23:49.983 --> 00:23:54.124
hobn zey dos alts dertseylt vi m'hot alemen avekgeharget, oysgeshosn.

00:23:54.804 --> 00:23:57.661
un dortn, undz hot men gebrakht in Telzher geto,

00:23:57.661 --> 00:23:59.884
zikh glaykh geshafn epes a komitet.

00:23:59.884 --> 00:24:02.404
(epes) darf dokh vern mit vemen onfirn.

00:24:02.404 --> 00:24:05.278
eyne iz geven aza Ester Blokh gedenk ikh.

00:24:05.570 --> 00:24:07.454
s'iz geven a dokter Blat.

00:24:07.781 --> 00:24:11.670
er iz nokh do mit di froy geven. tsu zey lebn ye veys ikh nit. ts-

00:24:13.485 --> 00:24:19.217
nu, m'hot gegebn dortn, ikh veys nit fun vanet, s'iz geven a bisl zakhn hobn zey gehat. m'hot tseteylt, gegebn zikh ontsuton,

00:24:19.678 --> 00:24:20.544
un s'iz geven

00:24:20.544 --> 00:24:23.750
un m'hot oyf, arayngez- m'hot aroysgehoybn di litviner

00:24:23.750 --> 00:24:25.978
vos zey hobn gelebt in di shtiblekh dortn,

00:24:25.978 --> 00:24:29.459
un dortn hot men arayngezetst di ale di finf hundert vos m'hot gebrakht

00:24:29.583 --> 00:24:30.944
fun GERULIAI.

00:24:33.465 --> 00:24:36.244
nu, dortn hobn mir gelebt a kurtse tsayt.

00:24:36.384 --> 00:24:37.951
eyn tsayt iz oykhet,

00:24:37.970 --> 00:24:39.078
s'flegn kumen,

00:24:39.405 --> 00:24:41.138
oyf arbet hot men undz gefirt.

00:24:42.088 --> 00:24:46.169
flegn kumen poyerim fun dorf, un me fleg nemen tsu grobn bulves.

00:24:46.205 --> 00:24:48.208
oyf di derfer flegn zey firn.

00:24:48.905 --> 00:24:51.509
zaynen mir oykh eyn mol arayngefaln in aza,

00:24:51.509 --> 00:24:52.798
akht meydlekh

00:24:52.989 --> 00:24:54.401
bay eynem a polyak.

00:24:55.385 --> 00:24:57.556
LAPINSKAS hot er geheysn.

00:24:59.672 --> 00:25:01.928
geven zeyer a shlekhter mentsh.

00:25:02.270 --> 00:25:03.921
o, er fleg geyn mit a

00:25:03.921 --> 00:25:06.132
a nagayke fleg men dos rufn aza,

00:25:06.132 --> 00:25:07.614
PA- PALKA.

00:25:08.396 --> 00:25:09.684
un er fleg zukhn

00:25:09.684 --> 00:25:11.681
tomer s'iz geblibn a bulve in der erd.

00:25:12.952 --> 00:25:16.237
az er fleg gefinen a bulve fleg men krign mit dos ibern rukn

00:25:16.361 --> 00:25:17.115
fun im.

00:25:18.116 --> 00:25:21.581
nu, un esn hobn zey gegebn. m'hot gelebt bay zey, baym po- bayn

00:25:21.626 --> 00:25:22.560
balebos.

00:25:22.588 --> 00:25:24.287
di tsayt vos m'hot gearbet

00:25:24.478 --> 00:25:26.211
hot men gelebt baym balebos.

00:25:27.566 --> 00:25:29.737
zaynen mir oykh etlekhe mol azoy geven

00:25:29.774 --> 00:25:30.699
geforn.

00:25:33.236 --> 00:25:37.230
nakhe-, eyn mol k- bin, ikh bin nit geven enlekh oyf keyn yidishe.

00:25:38.923 --> 00:25:41.702
fleg ikh aroysgeyn fun geto in shtot a mol.

00:25:41.739 --> 00:25:44.776
(kh'fleg khapn...) in geto zaynen mir arumgegangen mit di gele

00:25:44.776 --> 00:25:45.617
lates

00:25:46.382 --> 00:25:47.895
fornt un oyfn rukn.

00:25:47.985 --> 00:25:51.354
aroys in shtot hob ikh zikh dos aropgenumen fun zikh

00:25:52.322 --> 00:25:53.987
un ikh bin aroys in shtot.

00:25:54.853 --> 00:25:57.666
ikh hob gehat a ort epes bay vemen tsutsu- tsu geyn.

00:25:57.992 --> 00:26:00.568
un geyendik hob ikh getrofn a bakantn f-

00:26:00.962 --> 00:26:02.959
fun undzer shtetl, fun Kretinge.

00:26:02.959 --> 00:26:03.926
(er iz tsayt f-)

00:26:04.083 --> 00:26:05.093
a litviner.

00:26:04.623 --> 00:26:05.529
a krist.

00:26:05.093 --> 00:26:05.954
a krist.

00:26:05.954 --> 00:26:07.607
(er iz tsayt) far di

00:26:07.610 --> 00:26:09.582
sovyetishe makht bay undz dem yor.

00:26:09.582 --> 00:26:11.807
geven a, a po- a militsyoner,

00:26:11.947 --> 00:26:12.903
politsist.

00:26:15.474 --> 00:26:20.092
Maksimovitsh zayn familye. er hot nokh gelebt yetst oykh in Lite far undzer aroysforn.

00:26:22.140 --> 00:26:24.041
bin ikh tsu tsu im.

00:26:24.401 --> 00:26:26.423
kh'hob zikh forgeshtelt, ikh bin a Kretinger.

00:26:26.423 --> 00:26:27.956
zogt er, "gey mir nokh.

00:26:28.265 --> 00:26:29.289
kum mit mir."

00:26:30.881 --> 00:26:32.726
bin gegangen. bin ikh gegangen,

00:26:32.737 --> 00:26:34.503
nit klerndik keyn zakh.

00:26:34.712 --> 00:26:36.984
mir aroysgefirt hintern shtetl

00:26:37.715 --> 00:26:40.359
un aroyfgefirt oyf aza shtibele

00:26:40.753 --> 00:26:43.599
oyfn tsveytn etazh, oyf aza salke,

00:26:44.246 --> 00:26:48.510
arayn dortn bay zey in shtub, gezesn a froy mit a kleyne kind.

00:26:49.933 --> 00:26:52.290
nu, hob ikh im dertseylt di geshikhte

00:26:53.325 --> 00:26:54.349
az me f-

00:26:54.658 --> 00:26:58.719
me likvidirt, mir hobn gehert az me likvidirt in gikhn di Telzher geto,

00:26:58.978 --> 00:27:01.160
az in Shavl iz do a geto

00:27:01.160 --> 00:27:02.229
hobn mir zikh dervust,

00:27:04.074 --> 00:27:07.657
tsu er ken undz helfn antloyfn fun di geto, Telzh,

00:27:07.685 --> 00:27:10.261
un vi nit iz ariberfirn in Shavler geto

00:27:10.706 --> 00:27:14.736
vayle fun Shavler geto iz shoyn geven a farbindung mit Telzher geto.

00:27:14.756 --> 00:27:17.850
un mir hobn zikh dervust az mir hobn dortn gute bakante.

00:27:17.878 --> 00:27:19.225
undzere eltern's,

00:27:19.225 --> 00:27:21.281
nokh fun farn krig, fun Meml.

00:27:25.083 --> 00:27:26.731
un er iz geven maskem

00:27:27.277 --> 00:27:29.178
undz tsu helfn. vi?

00:27:30.264 --> 00:27:32.182
er hot gehat a bruder,

00:27:32.424 --> 00:27:34.646
gelebt hinter TELŠIAI in a dorf.

00:27:35.613 --> 00:27:37.413
in (aza) a shtetele, LUOKĖ.

00:27:37.740 --> 00:27:39.506
oyf yidish flegt men zogn Luknik.

00:27:41.958 --> 00:27:43.955
ober dem tog hot zeyer geregnt

00:27:43.955 --> 00:27:44.838
shreklekh,

00:27:45.536 --> 00:27:49.684
un er hot un- zogt er, "e- der bruder iz nito, ikh hob nit vi tsu geyn baym bruder,

00:27:49.684 --> 00:27:51.453
vos zikh ontsuton oyf di fis."

00:27:52.134 --> 00:27:54.305
bin ikh avek tsurik in geto.

00:27:54.817 --> 00:27:56.249
kh'hob genumen a por,

00:27:56.249 --> 00:27:58.097
nu, kalashn hot men dos gerufn

00:27:58.125 --> 00:27:59.098
a mol.

00:27:59.407 --> 00:28:00.788
kh'hob gebrakht.

00:28:02.495 --> 00:28:04.312
un er iz avek tsum bruder

00:28:04.959 --> 00:28:05.865
in dorf.

00:28:06.360 --> 00:28:07.738
az mir hobn opgeredt

00:28:08.148 --> 00:28:11.720
oyber der bruder iz maskem undz tsu firn in Shavl

00:28:11.777 --> 00:28:13.596
vayl der bruder hot zikh farnumen

00:28:13.596 --> 00:28:14.988
mitn arumforn

00:28:15.033 --> 00:28:16.777
fun dorf in Shavl.

00:28:16.805 --> 00:28:18.945
er flegt handlen, ikh veys nit genoy.

00:28:18.965 --> 00:28:22.115
yedn fals, oyber der bruder vet zayn maskem

00:28:22.239 --> 00:28:24.258
kumt er oyf morgn mit a fur

00:28:24.382 --> 00:28:25.186
mit ferd

00:28:25.901 --> 00:28:27.330
un er vet aykh nemen.

00:28:29.478 --> 00:28:30.589
oyf morgn

00:28:30.589 --> 00:28:32.612
bin ikh mit mayn kuzine Rokhl

00:28:32.955 --> 00:28:34.519
gekumen tsu im tsurik.

00:28:34.895 --> 00:28:36.729
mir geyen aroyf oyfn hoyf.

00:28:36.870 --> 00:28:38.079
shteyt a fur.

00:28:38.827 --> 00:28:39.508
tsvey gef-

00:28:39.508 --> 00:28:41.488
groyse ferd ayngeshpant,

00:28:42.067 --> 00:28:44.677
simen az er iz gekumen, er iz maskem.

00:28:46.860 --> 00:28:48.947
zaynen mir aroyf in shtub,

00:28:48.960 --> 00:28:50.566
hob ikh zikh dershrokn zeyer.

00:28:50.707 --> 00:28:52.153
gezesn a mentsh,

00:28:52.293 --> 00:28:54.076
groyse shvartse vontses,

00:28:54.572 --> 00:28:56.676
shvartse brenedike oygn.

00:28:57.542 --> 00:29:00.489
shreklekh, hot oysgezen gor vi, ikh veys nit vi tsu klern.

00:29:01.001 --> 00:29:02.919
yedn fals, er iz geven maskem

00:29:03.195 --> 00:29:05.215
undz es aribertsufirn.

00:29:07.903 --> 00:29:08.572
iz

00:29:09.185 --> 00:29:13.196
zaynen mir gekumen tsurik mit, mit zayn fur tsum geto

00:29:14.670 --> 00:29:19.103
un gezogt bay di vakh, er hot gezogt, er nemt undz oyf der arbet grobn bulves.

00:29:20.323 --> 00:29:22.134
do veln mir oyfhern.

00:29:22.134 --> 00:29:24.435
mir'n geyn toyshn a kaset.

00:29:24.677 --> 00:29:25.695
veln mir

00:29:25.695 --> 00:29:27.912
vayter geyn mit yene tsveyte kasete.
